19930416000000000_2	The first phase of the process is to extract the sludge and remove most of the water and then add this to bark sawdust and household waste to improve the consistency and increase the proportion of carbon.	first phase process extract sludg remov water add thi bark sawdust household wast improv consist increas proport carbon
19930416000000000_3	Air is then circulated through the mixture to create oxidation so that the organic matter breaks down.	air circul mixtur creat oxid organ matter break
